42 and is headquartered in Berlin, Germany. Springer Nature AG & Co. KGaA is a subsidiary of GvH Verm\u00f6gensverwaltungsgesellschaft Xxxiii mbH.", "Address": "Heidelberger Platz 3, Berlin, Germany, 14197", "AddressData": {"Street": "Heidelberger Platz 3", "City": "Berlin", "Country": "Germany", "ZIP": "14197"}, "Listings": {}, "Officers": {"0": {"Name": "Mr. Franciscus Vrancken Peeters", "Title": "CEO & Chairman of the Management Board", "YearBorn": "1966"}, "1": {"Name": "Ms. Alexandra  Dambeck", "Title": "CFO & Member of Management Board", "YearBorn": "1971"}, "2": {"Name": "Ms. Rachel  Jacobs", "Title": "Group General Counsel & Member of the Management Board", "YearBorn": "1975"}, "3": {"Name": "Dr. Harshavardhan  Jegadeesan", "Title": "Chief Publishing Officer & Member of the Management Board", "YearBorn": "1981"}, "4": {"Name": "Ms. Carolyn  Honour", "Title": "Chief Commercial Officer & Member of the Management Board", "YearBorn": "1960"}, "5": {"Name": "Mr. Marc  Spenle", "Title": "COO & Member of the Management Board", "YearBorn": "1972"}, "6": {"Name": "Mr. Matthias  Wissel", "Title": "Chief Information Officer", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "7": {"Name": "Ms. Ritu  Dhand", "Title": "Chief Scientific Officer", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "8": {"Name": "Mr. Tom  Waldron", "Title": "Head of Investor Relations", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "9": {"Name": "Ms. Maria  Castresana", "Title": "Chief People Officer", "YearBorn": "NA"}}, "Phone": "49 30 827 870", "WebURL": "https://www.springernature.com", "LogoURL": "", "FullTimeEmployees": 9200, "UpdatedAt": "2025-11-15"}, "Highlights": {"MarketCapitalization": 4618527744, "MarketCapitalizationMln": 4618.5277, "EBITDA": null, "PERatio": null, "PEGRatio": null, "WallStreetTargetPrice": 31.8286, "BookValue": null, "DividendShare": null, "DividendYield": null, "EarningsShare": null, "EPSEstimateCurrentYear": 1.1837, "EPSEstimateNextYear": 1.733, "EPSEstimateNextQuarter": 0, "EPSEstimateCurrentQuarter": 0, "MostRecentQuarter": "0000-00-00", "Prof